values:
Once while seeking my bliss,
I thought to give you a miss.
But I longed for your arms,
and all of your charms
and thought only of your sweet kiss.

They say every man is a star
but perhaps they've gone a bit far.
Shining at night,
under street light,
while the john's waiting out in his car.

There once was a white lab rat
who ran mazes in seconds flat
once he lost his way
missing a turn one day
and died in mortal combat.

There once was a kitten so fiesty
playing right next to my Ice Tea
he batted a mouse
all over the house
but sadly I wound up with Mice Tea

There once was a chap questing mysteries
in volumes of ancient histories
he could not resist temptation
after the first intiation
and now lectures on paranormal histories

there once was a girl named rufus
whose cat was a bit of a doofus.
up and down she ran
sat next to the fan
and her tail stuck up with a poofus.

There once was a cat named Crowley.
He considered himself quite holy.
He wrote many books
which got dirty looks.
And in his spare time drank Stoli.
